
=Reason 4: Adding an effects send & return=

'''1.''' Open up an empty Reason session and select the mixer. 




[[Image:Reason mixer selected.png|600px]]





'''2.''' Go to the create menu and select an effect such as a reverb or distortion module.



[[Image:Reason reverb select.png|600px]]






This should automatically connect the effects module as an aux send/return to the mixer. You can look at the connections by hitting the '''TAB''' button




[[Image:Reason reverb module connections.png|600px]]


